      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/1X/9aa33f53cd1ba61aa748b00887cafaa862745b3a.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/9aa33f53cd1ba61aa748b00887cafaa862745b3a\" title=\"IMG_2379.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/1X/9aa33f53cd1ba61aa748b00887cafaa862745b3a.JPG\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/9aa33f53cd1ba61aa748b00887cafaa862745b3a_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_2379.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">976×549 63.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Operacioni per rimarrjen e Mosulit nga ISIS ka nisur sot, sic ka deklaruar publikisht kryeministri iraken. Mosuli, qyteti i dyte me i madh ne Irak mendohet te jete kryeqyteti de-facto i Shtetit Islamik dhe i fundit ne Irak ku ISIS ende kontrollon territor. Premtimi per irakenet qe jetojne nen pushtetin e ISIS ne Mosul ishte se se shpejti do te festojne sebashku me trupat clirimtare ne rruget e qytetit.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
