      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"bsalaj\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"549\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/bsalaj/48/1491_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> bsalaj:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Operacioni per rimarrjen e Mosulit <strong>nga</strong> ISIS ka nisur sot,</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>si ta kuptojme kte?! qe isis po nis sulmin per marrjen e mosulit? mos duhej <strong>prej</strong> isis-it?!</p>",
